author: Emily Czachor
title: Military General Says Intelligence Remains 'Inconclusive' About Whether Coronavirus Came From Lab in Wuhan, But Evidence 'Leans Toward Natural'
description: United States Army General Mark Milley addressed questions about the new coronavirus' emergence from a Wuhan virology laboratory during a news conference Tuesday.
content:
Investigations into the coronavirus' origins suggest the disease emerged naturally, United States Army General Mark Milley said on Tuesday.
